      "text": "Everywhere serenity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 17000.0,
      "end_time": 22000.0,
      "text": "and a marvellous freedom from the tumult of the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31000.0,
      "end_time": 34000.0,
      "text": "Hi! I'm Emily, and I'm Sam,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34020.0,
      "end_time": 36000.0,
      "text": "we're here at Rievaulx Abbey."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 36020.0,
      "end_time": 39020.0,
      "text": "We're here to discover what it was like to"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 39020.0,
      "end_time": 41000.0,
      "text": "live in a medieval monastery. Let's go!"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 41000.0,
      "end_time": 44000.0,
      "text": "Ah, young pilgrims,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 44000.0,
      "end_time": 46000.0,
      "text": "my name is Aelred,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 46000.0,
      "end_time": 48000.0,
      "text": "and I am the Abbot of Rievaulx Abbey."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 48000.0,
      "end_time": 54500.0,
      "text": "Now I understand you that want to learn something about our way of life."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 54000.0,
      "end_time": 55000.0,
      "text": "Yes, correct."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 55000.0,
      "end_time": 57000.0,
      "text": "I think the best way to learn"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 57000.0,
      "end_time": 59000.0,
      "text": "about what it's like to be a monk"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 59000.0,
      "end_time": 62000.0,
      "text": "is to wear the same sort of clothes that monks wear."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 62000.0,
      "end_time": 64000.0,
      "text": "Would you like to come and dress as monks?"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 64000.0,
      "end_time": 65000.0,
      "text": "Yes please!"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 65000.0,
      "end_time": 67000.0,
      "text": "Then follow me."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 71000.0,
      "end_time": 75000.0,
      "text": "You look very, very smart now in your monks habits."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 75000.0,
      "end_time": 77000.0,
      "text": "Why are you called Aelred?"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 77000.0,
      "end_time": 82000.0,
      "text": "My name means, noble strength, it's Anglo Saxon."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 82000.0,
      "end_time": 90000.0,
      "text": "My family come from the north of England and for many years they have been devoted to the northern Saints, especially St Cuthbert."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 90000.0,
      "end_time": 92000.0,
      "text": "What does a Monk do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 92000.0,
      "end_time": 95900.0,
      "text": "When you become a Monk you leave the world behind"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 95000.0,
      "end_time": 98000.0,
      "text": "with all its riches, possessions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 98000.0,
      "end_time": 101000.0,
      "text": "your family and instead you come to an Abbey"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 101000.0,
      "end_time": 104000.0,
      "text": "and devote your life to the glory of God."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 104000.0,
      "end_time": 106000.0,
      "text": "What do you eat for breakfast?"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 106000.0,
      "end_time": 109000.0,
      "text": "We have one meal a day and that's normally the middle of the day"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 109000.0,
      "end_time": 113000.0,
      "text": "and that meal is a sort of... I suppose you would call it porridge."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 113000.0,
      "end_time": 117000.0,
      "text": "It's made of bread which we grind up."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 117000.0,
      "end_time": 120000.0,
      "text": "Then we add hot water."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 120000.0,
      "end_time": 125000.0,
      "text": "And then we add whatever vegetables we happen to have depending on the season."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 125000.0,
      "end_time": 128000.0,
      "text": "Some herbs, and maybe some fish."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 128000.0,
      "end_time": 132000.0,
      "text": "So what you end up with is a sort of porridge with vegetables and fish in it"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 132000.0,
      "end_time": 134000.0,
      "text": "and that's what we have to sustain us."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 134000.0,
      "end_time": 137000.0,
      "text": "Why are your robes white?"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 137020.0,
      "end_time": 142000.0,
      "text": "By wearing white, we are wearing the colour that wool is when it comes off a sheep's back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 142000.0,
      "end_time": 147000.0,
      "text": "so that makes it the cheapest so that's a way of showing that we believe very strongly in our vow of poverty."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 147020.0,
      "end_time": 151000.0,
      "text": "Do you have to be silent all the time and if you do how do you communicate?"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 151000.0,
      "end_time": 155000.0,
      "text": "Well St Benedict whose rule we follow"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 155000.0,
      "end_time": 162000.0,
      "text": "stresses that silence is very very important for Monks, because it stops us gossiping and lets us concentrate instead on God"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 162020.0,
      "end_time": 166000.0,
      "text": "so we're not allowed to speak at certain times of the day."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 166000.0,
      "end_time": 169000.0,
      "text": "We have a set of signs that we use to communicate with each other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 169000.0,
      "end_time": 171000.0,
      "text": "so that people still know what's going on."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 171000.0,
      "end_time": 174000.0,
      "text": "So see if you can guess what these might be the signs for."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 176000.0,
      "end_time": 178000.0,
      "text": "Is that fire?"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 178000.0,
      "end_time": 181000.0,
      "text": "Light out, candle?"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 181000.0,
      "end_time": 182000.0,
      "text": "Very good!"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 182000.0,
      "end_time": 183000.0,
      "text": "What about this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 183000.0,
      "end_time": 186000.0,
      "text": "Does that mean porridge?"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 186000.0,
      "end_time": 187000.0,
      "text": "Yes it does."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 187000.0,
      "end_time": 191000.0,
      "text": "So you see we can communicate with each other quite easily without the use of words."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 191000.0,
      "end_time": 192000.0,
      "text": "That's very clever."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 192020.0,
      "end_time": 193020.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 198000.0,
      "end_time": 202000.0,
      "text": "Well, you have done very, very well and you have learnt"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 202000.0,
      "end_time": 205000.0,
      "text": "all about the life of a Monk in the Abbey."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 205000.0,
      "end_time": 207000.0,
      "text": "But you face one final test."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 207000.0,
      "end_time": 211000.0,
      "text": "And that is the test of silence."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 211000.0,
      "end_time": 214000.0,
      "text": "So I challenge you, to see"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 214000.0,
      "end_time": 216000.0,
      "text": "who can be silent for longer?"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 216000.0,
      "end_time": 220000.0,
      "text": "So Emily, Sam, face each other"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 220000.0,
      "end_time": 222000.0,
      "text": "Begin!"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 230000.0,
      "end_time": 232000.0,
      "text": "And everything is peace,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 232000.0,
